snippet.title: DID YOU FEEL IT? 5.1 magnitude earthquake in North Carolina
snippet.description:
According to Chief Meteorologist Brad Panovich, a 5.1 magnitude earthquake was reported near Sparta, North Carolina which was the location of yesterday's 2.3. 

Panovich said this would be the biggest quake in North Carolina since the 5.1 magnitude in 1916 near Asheville. Panovich said Saturday's 2.6 magnitude in the same location was a foreshock. 

"I would expect many small aftershocks over the next few days," Panovich said.
https://www.wcnc.com/article/weather/did-you-feel-an-earthquake-in-charlotte/275-c4e0828a-6b8a-4d45-9b90-0f82b4297382

snippet.title: Beirut explosion: Video shows new angle of the massive blast
snippet.description:
Warning: This video contains disturbing content. Discretion advised. 
The moment of the massive explosion that rocked the Lebanese capital Beirut, killing more than 137 people and injuring thousands, was captured in high definition by a shop owner who was recording when the blast hit.

Video shows smoke rising from Beirut's port with small sparks being seen in what is believed to be fireworks that were set off by the blaze. According to reports, fireworks were stored in the same warehouse where 2,750 tons of ammonium nitrate had previously been stored. After several seconds of recording, a massive explosion bursts outwards, which then moves outwards towards where the shop owner is, the resulting shockwave impacting multiple buildings in the process.

For more info, please go to https://globalnews.ca/news/7256905/beirut-explosion-map-canada-cities/

snippet.title: Barcelona vs. Napoli | Champions League Round of 16 Highlights | UCL on CBS Sports
snippet.description:
Barcelona looked to keep their Champions League dreams alive at the Camp Nou against a young and talented Napoli side in their round of 16 second leg. 

And thanks to his expected brilliance, Messi's side advanced to the quarterfinals. 

A trio of first-half goals gave the La Liga side a 3-1 win over their opponent, providing a 4-2 aggregate win that saw Barcelona through to the final eight.

Lionel Messi, who had a lot on the line entering, scored a fantastic goal in the first half to help build an early 3-1 halftime advantage against their Serie A opposition. Luis Suarez and Clement Lenglet also contributed to the lead with goals of their own, while all Napoli was able to respond with was a penalty from Lorenzo Insigne. The halftime score held for the final 45, ensuring Barcelona's date with Bayern Munich on Friday.

Stream every UEFA Champions League match live on CBS All Access: https://www.cbs.com/shows/uefa-champions-league/

Subscribe to UCL on CBS Sports: https://www.youtube.com/UCLonCBSSports

snippet.description:
Hey Guys! By popular request, I am back with another video, fixing different art projects that I've done in past videos. I love re-painting and giving a makeover to different things that need some help, including stuff that I've ruined myself üòÇ 
These videos are also really fun because it's basically just a collection of different art activities that I like to do like squishy makeovers, painting on paint palettes and customizing things.

If you want to see the original creation of these items, here is where to find the videos:

Hey! my name is Moriah (pronounced muh-rye-yuh üòÇ ) and this is my channel....obviously. I'm 25 and like doing anything creative...and being snarky.....just a lil. I make a lot of decorating and painting videos here. I'm obsessed with editing and adding lil bits to my videos, so if that's not your thing....oof you may hate this haha. I paint on squishies, thrift store finds, and other random things I pick up. I also love to draw, but don't expect anything too skilled, I'm not the best at that haha. You will also find occasional crafting/testing crafting kits on my channel which are always a hot mess. And even some baking (REALLY bad at that, but it's fun to try LOL). 

CURRENT SERIES:
Squishy Makeovers: Fixing and decorating used squishies sent from my viewers
Thrift Store Makeovers: Fixing and decorating stuff I find at thrift stores/yard sales
Bake With ME: Recreating squishies I've decorated in real life
Create This Book: Drawing in the prompt book that I wrote (available to purchase and follow along)
Squishy Unboxing: Opening used squishy packages sent from viewers
Craft Kit Testing: pretty self explanatory. testing craft kits.

localizations.en.description:
Hey Guys! By popular request, I am back with another video, fixing different art projects that I've done in past videos. I love re-painting and giving a makeover to different things that need some help, including stuff that I've ruined myself üòÇ 
These videos are also really fun because it's basically just a collection of different art activities that I like to do like squishy makeovers, painting on paint palettes and customizing things.

If you want to see the original creation of these items, here is where to find the videos:
"Face of Failure" Squishy Girl: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0PTOoZAgr6Y&t=869s&ab_channel=MoriahElizabeth
Hydro Dipped Palette and Container: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eaLrWkWuDjw&t=352s&ab_channel=MoriahElizabeth


Sign up for the mailing list on my new online store to get early access to new products:
https://moriahelizabethmerch.com/

___________WELCOME TO MY CHANNEL__________

Hey! my name is Moriah (pronounced muh-rye-yuh üòÇ ) and this is my channel....obviously. I'm 25 and like doing anything creative...and being snarky.....just a lil. I make a lot of decorating and painting videos here. I'm obsessed with editing and adding lil bits to my videos, so if that's not your thing....oof you may hate this haha. I paint on squishies, thrift store finds, and other random things I pick up. I also love to draw, but don't expect anything too skilled, I'm not the best at that haha. You will also find occasional crafting/testing crafting kits on my channel which are always a hot mess. And even some baking (REALLY bad at that, but it's fun to try LOL). 

CURRENT SERIES:
Squishy Makeovers: Fixing and decorating used squishies sent from my viewers
Thrift Store Makeovers: Fixing and decorating stuff I find at thrift stores/yard sales
Bake With ME: Recreating squishies I've decorated in real life
Create This Book: Drawing in the prompt book that I wrote (available to purchase and follow along)
Squishy Unboxing: Opening used squishy packages sent from viewers
Craft Kit Testing: pretty self explanatory. testing craft kits.



___UPLOAD SCHEDULE___

Every Friday at 4:00pm ET: Alternating Squishy Makeovers, Thrift Makeovers, Craft Kit Reviews, Create This Book, Mail Openings and Miscellaneous crafts and DIYs

snippet.title: Bayern Munich vs. Chelsea | Champions League Round of 16 Highlights | UCL on CBS Sports
snippet.description:
Holding firm to a 3-0 aggregate lead heading into the second leg, Bayern did not need to prove much vs. a hobbled Chelsea side. But that didn't stop them from putting on a show.

Bayern Munich are through to the Champions League quarterfinals after thumping Chelsea on Saturday. Bayern Munich won the second leg, 4-1, with Robert Lewandowski scoring twice. The Bundesliga winners came into the second leg with a 3-0 advantage, so they ended up with a 7-1 aggregate edge over their Premier League opponent.

The German side was able to capitalize on their first leg momentum early as Lewandowski, the competition's leading score, earned a penalty kick in the 10th minute and converted the attempt. Bayern added goals throughout with Ivan Perisic scoring in the 24th minute, and Corentin Tolisso adding to the scoreline fresh off the bench during the 76th minute. Lewandowski headed home the 13th goal of his Champions League campaign in the 84th minute. Bayern will face Barcelona in the quarter final.

Stream every UEFA Champions League match live on CBS All Access: https://www.cbs.com/shows/uefa-champions-league/

Subscribe to UCL on CBS Sports: youtube.com/UCLonCBSSports

snippet.title: Beirut explosion: Video shows new angle of the massive blast
snippet.description:
Warning: This video contains disturbing content. Discretion advised. 
The moment of the massive explosion that rocked the Lebanese capital Beirut, killing more than 137 people and injuring thousands, was captured in high definition by a shop owner who was recording when the blast hit.

Video shows smoke rising from Beirut's port with small sparks being seen in what is believed to be fireworks that were set off by the blaze. According to reports, fireworks were stored in the same warehouse where 2,750 tons of ammonium nitrate had previously been stored. After several seconds of recording, a massive explosion bursts outwards, which then moves outwards towards where the shop owner is, the resulting shockwave impacting multiple buildings in the process.

For more info, please go to https://globalnews.ca/news/7256905/beirut-explosion-map-canada-cities/

snippet.title: thank you for everything
snippet.description:
In 1995 I was born into a very different world to the one we live in now. The internet was brand new and YouTube hadn‚Äôt even been thought of yet! I set out making this video to say thank you for two hundred thousand subscribers. But...
As I delved into our photo albums it evolved into a story of our lives; hopefully proving that although we have experienced a very positive stint on this planet, life is never plain sailing. The death of my grandmother left undealt trauma and only recently have I truly understood that loss, remembering the beautiful face I loved as a child. The section of video at 2:39 portrays an unfortunate experience at school which led to bullying and ending up a somewhat disturbed child. Discovering fishing soon after was monumental to our progression and it helped the both of us find peace, focus and eventually a career path. I believe nature can help people and that is what drives us to inspire others to get outside with these videos. YouTube has been our ‚Äòthing‚Äô now for over 13 years, and we can‚Äôt quite believe the joy and excitement it has brought us, especially since leaving our jobs and going full time. Feel free to click subscribe and join our journey be it fishing, aquatics, adventures or gardening. The future is brighter than the past ever was! 
From Carl (by the way, that's my mum's piano at the end! She finally got a piano and learnt how to play!) 
Follow us on Instagram: http://instagram.com/carlandalex
Chat with us on Facebook: https://facebook.com/carlandalex
Our channel, Carl and Alex Fishing was launched in 2013. Our aim was to inspire people to go fishing and enjoy the outdoors. Over the years we have fished in freshwater, saltwater and also enjoy keeping pet fish. Subscribe to our channel for regular exciting videos!

snippet.title: 2020 PGA Championship Round 3 Highlights: Dustin Johnson leads after 54 | CBS Sports HQ
snippet.description:
A star-studded Moving Day at the 2020 PGA Championship saw nearly a handful of players tied for the lead at one point. By the end of the day, there were 11 golfers within three strokes of the lead heading into Sunday's final round at TPC Harding Park. 

The first major championship of 2020 has nearly guaranteed a must-see finish with Dustin Johnson holding the 54-hole lead at 9 under while Brooks Koepka, Jason Day, Bryson DeChambeau and Tony Finau are among those still in striking distance. Of course, established names aren't the only ones in the mix as Scottie Scheffler, Cameron Champ and Collin Morikawa are among those who would love to kickstart their budding careers with a major win on Sunday afternoon in San Francisco. 

Saturday's round was a tribute to the challenge that TPC Harding Park provides. D.J., Scheffler and Morikawa soared to the top of the leaderboard by posting 65s, but the late-afternoon groups were left grinding through foggy, windy conditions that made scoring difficult. Of the final four pairings on the course only two players, Champ and Koepka, scored under par on Saturday.

snippet.title: Boatbuilding - Lining-out for Planking (EP78)
snippet.description:
Rebuilding a historic sailing yacht - Lining-out for Planking  (EP78)
Support; http://www.sampsonboat.co.uk/support
Become a Patron; http://www.patreon.com/sampsonboatco

---- 

EPISODE 78.
In this episode we calculate the locations and sizes of all the hull planks, based on the complex shape of the hull. I‚Äôve never done this before, so we get some help from the Lead Shipwright on the Western Flyer Project (Shipwrights Co-Op, PT).
I‚Äôm also very excited to welcome two new members to the team - Rosie, who is going to be in an apprentice-style role, and Charlie, who is going to be helping out with video production!

snippet.title: The Italian Job Lamborghini Miura - First time back in The Alps! | Tyrrell's Classic Workshop
snippet.description:
In a very special episode of Tyrrell's Classic Workshop, Iain looks back on a career highlight with one of the World's most famous cars, the Lamborghini Miura from the opening sequence of the Italian Job movie!  Having gone to great lengths to establish the authenticity of the vehicle, it was brought to Iain's workshop for a tune-up.  And that could have been the end of the story... but it wasn't, you'll just have to watch to discover what happened next!

Iain's recording of Matt Monro's iconic track, "On Days Like These", is available to stream or purchase on various sites now including iTunes, Amazon, Spotify and Deezer.  All of Iain and Steve's royalties from any sales will be donated to charity.
Buy on iTunes - https://music.apple.com/gb/album/on-days-like-these-2020-remix-feat-steve-wright-single/1526827877

Stream on Spotify - https://open.spotify.com/track/5SwVby9XRv6KAdmMutT7dC?si=PUnrv1WxTBSshEzu-ekkaA

Thank you once again to everyone for the overwhelming reception of these videos and for all the support of likes, subscribes and wonderful comments.

snippet.title: Lesti - Kulepas Dengan Ikhlas | Official Music Video
snippet.description:
Lesti - Kulepas Dengan Ikhlas | Official Music Video

#Lesti #LestiBillar #MusicVideo #Lagubarulesti #laguadibal #videodangdutterbaru

Selepas merilis lagu bertemakan patah hati yang mendalam beberapa bulan lalu, kini Lesti kembali melahirkan sebuah karya baru dengan tema ‚ÄòKeikhlasan‚Äô.  Dibawah naungan label rekaman 3D Entertainment dan manajemen artis STREAM Entertainment, single berjudul ‚ÄòKulepas Dengan Ikhlas‚Äô dirilis tepat dihari ulang tahun Lesti, 5 Agustus 2020, melalui music video di channel youtube 3D Entertainment.

Setelah sebelumnya kisah Lesti dikait-kaitkan dengan aktor Rizky Billar, yang memiliki background kisah cinta yang sama, dalam music video Lesti terbaru pun, keduanya dipertemukan. 

Adegan dalam music video tersebut sangat berkaitan dengan lirik yang diciptakan Adibal, penuh keikhlasan. Berangkat dari rasa simpati yang mendalam dan kedekatan secara pribadi, secara khusus Adibal Sahrul menciptakan lagu untuk Lesti.  ‚ÄúLagu ini saya tulis tepat tanggal 17 Juli saat melihat postingan Lesti menghadiri pernikahan Rizky DA, cukup cepat bikinnya 1 jam aja... mungkin karena saya cukup dekat dengan mereka berdua, jadi saya dapat meraba apa yang mungkin mereka rasakan, khususnya Lesti, Kesan saya , lesti itu punya hati yg kuat ,apapun alasannya , gak mudah pastinya berada dalam situasi itu,‚Äù tutur Adibal.

Lagu ini terasa paket lengkap dari sisi lirik, balutan musik yang menyentuh hati dan diperankan langsung oleh sosok yang mengalami kisahnya dan sebuah music video.  Semoga pesan besar dalam lagu ini dapat tersampaikan yaitu kita boleh merencanakan apa saja, pada akhirnya Tuhan yang menentukan.

#Lesti #LestiBillar #MusicVideo #Lagubarulesti #laguadibal #videodangdutterbaru

Selepas merilis lagu bertemakan patah hati yang mendalam beberapa bulan lalu, kini Lesti kembali melahirkan sebuah karya baru dengan tema ‚ÄòKeikhlasan‚Äô.  Dibawah naungan label rekaman 3D Entertainment dan manajemen artis STREAM Entertainment, single berjudul ‚ÄòKulepas Dengan Ikhlas‚Äô dirilis tepat dihari ulang tahun Lesti, 5 Agustus 2020, melalui music video di channel youtube 3D Entertainment.

Setelah sebelumnya kisah Lesti dikait-kaitkan dengan aktor Rizky Billar, yang memiliki background kisah cinta yang sama, dalam music video Lesti terbaru pun, keduanya dipertemukan. 

Adegan dalam music video tersebut sangat berkaitan dengan lirik yang diciptakan Adibal, penuh keikhlasan. Berangkat dari rasa simpati yang mendalam dan kedekatan secara pribadi, secara khusus Adibal Sahrul menciptakan lagu untuk Lesti.  ‚ÄúLagu ini saya tulis tepat tanggal 17 Juli saat melihat postingan Lesti menghadiri pernikahan Rizky DA, cukup cepat bikinnya 1 jam aja... mungkin karena saya cukup dekat dengan mereka berdua, jadi saya dapat meraba apa yang mungkin mereka rasakan, khususnya Lesti, Kesan saya , lesti itu punya hati yg kuat ,apapun alasannya , gak mudah pastinya berada dalam situasi itu,‚Äù tutur Adibal.

Lagu ini terasa paket lengkap dari sisi lirik, balutan musik yang menyentuh hati dan diperankan langsung oleh sosok yang mengalami kisahnya dan sebuah music video.  Semoga pesan besar dalam lagu ini dapat tersampaikan yaitu kita boleh merencanakan apa saja, pada akhirnya Tuhan yang menentukan.

snippet.title: [LIVE HD] NDP 2020: Singapore holds parade with salute to frontliners in COVID-19 battle
snippet.description:
On Aug 9, 2020, Singapore marked 55 years of independence with a scaled-down National Day Parade, dedicated to frontline workers on the forefront of the fight against the COVID-19 pandemic. The parade segment of NDP 2020 took place at the Padang and featured a 'Roar of unity' flypast by F-15SG fighter planes and a mobile column which went through the heartlands.

snippet.title: Beirut explosion - mushroom shaped blast rips through Lebanese capital
snippet.description:
A massive explosion has killed at least ten people and left hundreds injured after the blast devastated part of Lebanon's capital Beirut.

Pictures show buildings destroyed, people walking wounded, and a sea of wreckage after the blast that could be heard some 125 miles away in Cyprus.

Lebanon's state news agency NNA and two security sources said the blast had occurred in the port area where there are warehouses housing explosives, reports Reuters.

Nearby buildings around the port have been leveled, windows and doors have been blown out, and fires burn as smoke plumes billow across Beirut.

The Government Palace - the home of Lebanon's PM Hassan Diab - was damaged in the blast, and his wife and daughter were injured in the explosion.

snippet.title: Beirut explosion: Video shows new angle of the massive blast
snippet.description:
Warning: This video contains disturbing content. Discretion advised. 
The moment of the massive explosion that rocked the Lebanese capital Beirut, killing more than 137 people and injuring thousands, was captured in high definition by a shop owner who was recording when the blast hit.

Video shows smoke rising from Beirut's port with small sparks being seen in what is believed to be fireworks that were set off by the blaze. According to reports, fireworks were stored in the same warehouse where 2,750 tons of ammonium nitrate had previously been stored. After several seconds of recording, a massive explosion bursts outwards, which then moves outwards towards where the shop owner is, the resulting shockwave impacting multiple buildings in the process.

For more info, please go to https://globalnews.ca/news/7256905/beirut-explosion-map-canada-cities/

Lebanon is in mourning after a huge explosion in the capital Beirut killed at least 78 people and injured more than 4,000 others on Tuesday. The whole city was shaken by the blast, which began with a fire at the port which exploded into a mushroom cloud. President Michel Aoun said 2,750 tonnes of ammonium nitrate had been stored unsafely in a warehouse for six years. He scheduled an urgent cabinet meeting for Wednesday, and said a two-week state of emergency should be declared. The country will observe an official period of mourning for three days from Wednesday.

snippet.title: What Makes Singapore's National Day 2020 Celebration Remarkable? | On The Red Dot | Full Episode
snippet.description:
This year, Singapore's National Day Parade is facing its greatest challenge ever. As the country turns 55 in the wake of a global pandemic, social-distancing measures mean there will be no mass displays, no grand platforms and no spectators in the thousands. Instead, it's being scaled back and split up, with the iconic state flag flypast taken into the heartlands. How will the participants pull together and deliver a show to remember of the times today?

snippet.title: INSANE LEVEL 100 Monster Curry Challenge! | RECORD SMASHED! | Spiciest Curry Rice in Singapore!
snippet.description:
For this video, I present to you my attempts at the Monster Curry Level 100 Spicy Challenge! The challenge involves completing a plate of their standard Chicken/Pork Katsu Curry Rice, except the curry is topped with a deadly-looking black concoction made from ridiculously spicy chillies. For those spice-averse, eating the first few bites might make the challenge seem doable, but the excruciating burning sensation kicks in after a minute. Completing it in under 10 minutes makes the dish free.

It was a true challenge for me due to my well-known low spice tolerance, but I grit my teeth and took it one bite (sometimes two) at a time, attempting this for a total of 6 times. Initially my time was in the 1-2 minute range, but by the end I was able to do it sub 1-min, with my final attempt being my best time at 52.13s and also the best ranked time for this challenge.

Check out the end for a bonus clip of Mervin attempting the challenge!

Connect with me!
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/zermattneofls
Instagram - http://instagram.com/zermattneo

snippet.title: Beirut explosion: Massive blast devastates city's port area
snippet.description:
A massive explosion shook Lebanon‚Äôs capital of Beirut on Tuesday, devastating the city's port area, with the blast billowing smoke over the city.  Lebanon‚Äôs internal security chief Abbas Ibrahim said the blast happened in a section that housed highly-explosive materials. Crystal Goomansingh reports.

According to Reuters, at least 10 people have been found dead following the explosion. The Lebanese Red Cross said hundreds of people were also taken to hospitals for treatment, but many remain trapped in homes damaged by the explosion.

The deadly explosion comes at a time when Lebanon is experiencing its worst economic and financial crisis in decades.

It also comes amid rising tensions between Israel and the militant Hezbollah group along Lebanon‚Äôs southern border.

snippet.title: Beirut explosion: Video shows new angle of the massive blast
snippet.description:
Warning: This video contains disturbing content. Discretion advised. 
The moment of the massive explosion that rocked the Lebanese capital Beirut, killing more than 137 people and injuring thousands, was captured in high definition by a shop owner who was recording when the blast hit.

Video shows smoke rising from Beirut's port with small sparks being seen in what is believed to be fireworks that were set off by the blaze. According to reports, fireworks were stored in the same warehouse where 2,750 tons of ammonium nitrate had previously been stored. After several seconds of recording, a massive explosion bursts outwards, which then moves outwards towards where the shop owner is, the resulting shockwave impacting multiple buildings in the process.

For more info, please go to https://globalnews.ca/news/7256905/beirut-explosion-map-canada-cities/

snippet.title: Beirut explosion: Massive blast devastates city's port area
snippet.description:
A massive explosion shook Lebanon‚Äôs capital of Beirut on Tuesday, devastating the city's port area, with the blast billowing smoke over the city.  Lebanon‚Äôs internal security chief Abbas Ibrahim said the blast happened in a section that housed highly-explosive materials. Crystal Goomansingh reports.

According to Reuters, at least 10 people have been found dead following the explosion. The Lebanese Red Cross said hundreds of people were also taken to hospitals for treatment, but many remain trapped in homes damaged by the explosion.

The deadly explosion comes at a time when Lebanon is experiencing its worst economic and financial crisis in decades.

It also comes amid rising tensions between Israel and the militant Hezbollah group along Lebanon‚Äôs southern border.

snippet.title: Beirut explosion - mushroom shaped blast rips through Lebanese capital
snippet.description:
A massive explosion has killed at least ten people and left hundreds injured after the blast devastated part of Lebanon's capital Beirut.

Pictures show buildings destroyed, people walking wounded, and a sea of wreckage after the blast that could be heard some 125 miles away in Cyprus.

Lebanon's state news agency NNA and two security sources said the blast had occurred in the port area where there are warehouses housing explosives, reports Reuters.

Nearby buildings around the port have been leveled, windows and doors have been blown out, and fires burn as smoke plumes billow across Beirut.

The Government Palace - the home of Lebanon's PM Hassan Diab - was damaged in the blast, and his wife and daughter were injured in the explosion.

Lebanon is in mourning after a huge explosion in the capital Beirut killed at least 78 people and injured more than 4,000 others on Tuesday. The whole city was shaken by the blast, which began with a fire at the port which exploded into a mushroom cloud. President Michel Aoun said 2,750 tonnes of ammonium nitrate had been stored unsafely in a warehouse for six years. He scheduled an urgent cabinet meeting for Wednesday, and said a two-week state of emergency should be declared. The country will observe an official period of mourning for three days from Wednesday.

Und heute wird‚Äôs s√º√ü:

K√∂stliches Schichtdessert mit Cr√™pes, Brownie und Marmelade | Dieses¬†Schichtdessert¬†ist ein wahr gewordener Traum f√ºr alle, die¬†Cr√™pes¬†lieben. Dank eines Tricks mit einem leeren Milchkarton bereiten wir das leckerste Cr√™pe-Dessert aller Zeiten zu. Es besteht aus einem¬†Brownie, schokoladigen Cr√™pes, wei√üer Creme und¬†Marmelade. Am Ende wird alles mit einer knackigen Ganache √ºbergossen ‚Äì fertig ist dieses leckere geschichtete Wunder. üòã

M√∂chtest du weitere Rezepte wie diese sehen? Dann abonniere unseren Kanal, um keine neuen Videos mehr zu verpassen: https://www.youtube.com/c/leckerschmecker?sub_confirmation=1

Hier kommst du zum Rezept: https://www.leckerschmecker.me/schichtdessert-mit-crepes/?&ref=yt

Auf Pinterest merken: https://bit.ly/2AW9bhs

*************************************************

Daf√ºr brauchst du:

300 g Mehl
75 g Kakao
3 Eier
300 ml Milch
300 ml Mineralwasser
1 TL Salz
3 EL Zucker

F√ºr die Creme:
400 g wei√üe, gehackte Kuvert√ºre
240 ml Vollmilch
100 g weiche Butter
300 g sehr steif geschlagene Sahne

F√ºr die Ganache:
300 g Zartbitterschokolade
300 g Sahne
10 g weiche Butter

Au√üerdem:
fertigen Brownie (gekauft oder selbst gebacken)
rote Marmelade
geraspelte Schokolade
2 aufgeschnittene 1-l-Milchpackungen

So geht es:

1. Als Erstes bereitest du die Creme zu. Erhitze die Milch auf ca. 60 ¬∞C und gie√üe sie √ºber die klein gehackte, wei√üe¬†Schokolade. Wenn die Schokolade etwas abgek√ºhlt ist, gib weiche Butter in St√ºcken hinzu. Verr√ºhre alles mit einem Schneebesen. Am Schluss hebst du die steif geschlagene Sahne unter. Wenn du 2-3 Blatt Gelatine einarbeitest, ist die Creme auf jeden Fall fester und h√§lt sp√§ter besser beim Zusammenbau. Die Creme muss anschlie√üend f√ºr mindestens 2 Stunden im K√ºhlschrank abk√ºhlen.
2. Dann bereitest du die Schoko-Cr√™pes¬†zu. Vermische Mehl mit Kakao und f√ºge Ei, Salz, Zucker und Milch hinzu. R√ºhre mit einem Schneebesen alles glatt. Gib das Mineralwasser hinzu und verr√ºhre alles noch einmal. Decke den Teig ab und lasse ihn f√ºr 30 Minuten ruhen. Pinsle eine Pfanne mit √ñl ein und backe die Cr√™pes darin aus.
3. Nun wird die Ganache zubereitet. Erw√§rme die Sahne auf ca. 60 ¬∞C und gie√üe sie √ºber die gehackte Schokolade. Lasse die Schokolade schmelzen und gib Butter hinzu. Vermische alles miteinander. Stelle die Ganache dann erst einmal beiseite.
4. Nun beginnt die ‚ÄûSchichtarbeit‚Äú: Schneide beide Milchkartons der L√§nge nach auf, wie im folgenden Bild zu sehen, und lege einen der beiden mit zurechtgeschnittenem Brownie-Teig aus.
5. Schneide die Schoko-Cr√™pes in der Pfanne zurecht. Verwende dabei am besten den anderen aufgeschnittenen Milchkarton als Schablone.
6. Gib die wei√üe Creme auf den Brownieboden im Milchkarton und verteile sie mit einem L√∂ffel.
7. Verteile einen Essl√∂ffel¬†Marmelade¬†in der Mitte auf der Creme.
8. Lege nun einen zurechtgeschnittenen Cr√™pe in die H√§lfte des noch leeren Milchkartons.
9. Lege einen weiteren zurechtgeschnittenen Cr√™pe in den Milchkarton, in dem schon der Brownieboden und die Creme sind.
10. Verteile in beiden H√§lften eine Schicht wei√üe Creme. Gib in den Karton, in dem nur der Cr√™pe und Creme sind, etwas Marmelade in der Mitte.
11. Rasple ein wenig Schokolade in den anderen Karton.
12. Dann kommt wieder je eine Schicht Cr√™pe, wei√üe Creme, Marmelade sowie Schokoraspel in beide Kartons. Klappe anschlie√üend beide Kartonh√§lften aufeinander und l√∂se die Verpackungen vorsichtig vom Inhalt. Bestreiche das Dessert nochmal mit der wei√üen Creme und √ºbergie√üe es mit der Ganache. Stelle das Cr√™pe-Dessert vor dem Servieren ein paar Stunden kalt.

Guten Appetit!

snippet.description:
Eine Zeitreise durch das vergangene Jahrhundert des Motorsports: Das ist der AvD-Oldtimer-Grand-Prix! Mehrere hundert Rennwagen machen den #avdogp auch dieses Jahr zu einem wahren Festival des historischen Motorsports. Auf Grund einer Ausnahmegenehmigung der Kreisverwaltung Ahrweiler sind bis zu 5.000 Besucher pro Tag zugelassen. 

Jacky Ickx (BEL) und Ren√© Arnoux (FRA) geh√∂ren zu den prominentesten Piloten im neuen Formel-1-Demolauf, bei dem vor allem Ferarri-F1-Boliden der 70er- bis 90er-Jahre antreten. Historische Sport- und Tourenwagen sowie GTs, die in die Historie von Le Mans ebenso entf√ºhren wie etwa in die DTM- und DRM-Geschichte, machen das historische Motorsporterlebnis perfekt. 

Dazu kommen die Vorkriegsrennwagen der ‚ÄûVintage Sports Car Trophy‚Äú, die bis in die Gr√ºndertage der legend√§ren Eifelstrecke zur√ºckreichen. Und mit den Ferraris der FCD Racing Series und den Boliden des International Audi R8 LMS-Cup gibt es sogar Ausfl√ºge in den aktuellen Motorsport.
